      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for clarifying. i guess i'm just nervous about the 'unforeseen' side of things. besides just standard damage, what are some of the more unusual or difficult-to-claim scenarios during ocean freight? like, what kind of things do people usually struggle to get covered when cargo goes missing in unexpected ways?",
